* [[Medway College of Design]], Fashion.<ref name=":4">{{Cite book|title = 50 Women Artists You Should Know|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XS0yAQAAIAAJ|publisher=Prestel|date=1 January 2008|isbn=9783791339566|first=Christiane|last=Weidemann|page=162}}</ref>
* [[Royal College of Art]], M.A. in painting.<ref>{{cite web|title=Tracey Emin|url=http://www.rca.ac.uk/studying-at-the-rca/the-rca-experience/student-voices/rca-luminaries/tracey-emin|website=rca.ac.uk|accessdate=20 February 2016}}</ref>
* [[Kent Institution of Art|Kent Institution of Art & Design]].{{clarify|date=January 2016}}
